-- EU's Rehn Says Has Full Confidence in Ireland Will Repair Financial System
-- Gabi Thesing
-- 2010-09-20T09:03:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/eu-s-rehn-says-has-full-confidence-in-ireland-will-repair-financial-system.html

          
          
             European Union Economic and
Monetary Affairs Commissioner Olli Rehn said he is confident
Irish authorities will be able to “repair” the nation’s
financial system.  
 Speaking today at an event in Tallinn, Estonia, Rehn also
said that proposed new sanctions for EU deficit offenders will
be based on current EU treaties.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Gabi Thesing in Tallinn, Estonia, at 
 gthesing@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        